50
00:02:55.561 --> 00:02:56.715
What makes a great leader?

51
00:02:56.715 --> 00:02:58.561
What makes you stand out from the crowd?

52
00:02:58.561 --> 00:03:01.418
Let me tell you.

53
00:03:01.418 --> 00:03:03.561
