58
00:03:17.361 --> 00:03:20.561
You're going to have to amp it up.

59
00:03:20.561 --> 00:03:23.186
Leaders need to be great communicators.

60
00:03:23.186 --> 00:03:27.561
One of your most important skills will need improvement on.

61
00:03:27.561 --> 00:03:32.561
It is hard to imagine a successful leader who is not a good communicator.

62
00:03:32.561 --> 00:03:34.208
As a software engineer,

63
00:03:34.208 --> 00:03:38.737
you may not have considered how important communicating with others is,

64
00:03:38.737 --> 00:03:45.561
