66
00:03:49.561 --> 00:03:53.561
You will now be the rainmaker and therefore the influencer.

67
00:03:53.561 --> 00:03:54.761
Managing customer expectations.

68
00:03:54.761 --> 00:03:57.561
The customer and stakeholder should never be

69
